{{Unreferenced stub|auto=yes|date=December 2009}}
The '''Czech Ice Hockey Hall of Fame''' was founded in 2008 and is located in [[Prague]], [[Czech Republic]]. The Hall honors individuals that have contributed to the sport of [[ice hockey|hockey]] in the Czech Republic.  It houses displays and a collection of memorabilia depicting the significant contributions of [[player (game)|players]], [[coach (ice hockey)|coaches]], [[official (ice hockey)|referees]] and other important figures in the sport.

