'''Ferki Aliu Stadium''' ({{lang-sq|Stadiumi Ferki Aliu}}), is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Vushtrri]], [[Kosovo]]. It is currently used for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[KF Kosova Vushtrri]] of the [[Kosovar Superliga]]. The stadium holds 6,000 people.

