{{Infobox sport tournament |year = 2011 |name = Germany's Strongest Man |image = |location = Germany |establishment = 1994? |format = Multi-event competition |purse = |month_played = <!--Use if still played--> |current_champion = {{flagicon|Germany}} [[Daniel Wildt]] }}
'''Germany's Strongest Man''' ({{lang-de|Stärkster Mann Deutschlands}}) is an annual [[Strongman (strength athlete)|strongman]] competition held in [[Germany]] and featuring exclusively German athletes. [[Heinz Ollesch]] holds the record for most wins with 12 wins.
