'''Hatta Club''' is a sports club based in [[Hatta, United Arab Emirates|Hatta]] in the [[Emirate of Dubai]], [[United Arab Emirates|UAE]] founded in 1981. It is most widely known for its professional football team, which currently plays in the [[UAE Arabian Gulf League]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=HATTA CLUB |url=https://int.soccerway.com/teams/united-arab-emirates/hatta-dubai/9067/ |publisher=soccerway.com |accessdate=31 July 2017}}</ref>

