The '''Honduran National Cycling Federation''' (in [[Spanish language|Spanish]]: ''Federación Nacional de Ciclismo de Honduras'') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Honduras]].

It is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and [[Confederacion Panamericana de Ciclismo|COPACI]].

