{{Coord|47|11|5|N|19|47|34|E|display=title}} {{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Malomtó széli stadion | image = | location = [[Cegléd]], [[Hungary]] | coordinates = | dimensions = 110 x 64 meters | broke_ground = | opened = 3 July 1926 | renovated = | closed = | demolished = | owner = | operator = | construction_cost = | architect = | former_names = | tenants = [[Ceglédi VSE]] | seating_capacity = 4,000 }}
'''Malomtó széli stadion''' is a sports stadium in [[Cegléd]], [[Hungary]]. The stadium is home to the [[association football]] club [[Ceglédi VSE]]. The stadium has a capacity of 4,000.
