[[Image:Skinner knife.jpg|thumb|300px|skinner knife]]
The skinner knife or skinning knife is a professional tool for a [[Skinner (profession)|skinner]]. Typically a skinner knife has wide, short blade. The edge is strong and does not have much flexibility or spring. Skinning knives are more a [[hunting]] tool than a weapon.

